Package: lymphclon
Version: 1.3.0
Date: 2014-11-06
Title: Accurate Estimation of Clonal Coincidences and Abundances from Biological Replicates
Authors@R: c(person(given = "Yi", family = "Liu", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "liuyipei@gmail.com"),
